hc.server.ui

Class ClientSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • hc.server.ui.ClientSession

  • public class ClientSession
extends Object
    a ClientSession instance will be created before ProjectContext.EVENT_SYS_MOBILE_LOGIN, and will be released after ProjectContext.EVENT_SYS_MOBILE_LOGOUT.
    a ProjectContext instance will be created before ProjectContext.EVENT_SYS_PROJ_STARTUP, and will be released after ProjectContext.EVENT_SYS_PROJ_SHUTDOWN.

    invoke ProjectContext.getClientSession() to get it.

    Important :
    in the future implementation, multiple users (same account) are online at same time, so please let project to project, user to user.

    ClientSession is thread safe.
    Since:
    7.7
